Find first and last digits of a number
Given a number and to find first and last digit of a number.
Examples: 
 

Input : 12345 
Output : First digit: 1
         last digit : 5

Input : 98562
Output : First digit: 9
         last digit : 2


public class MyClass 
{
	//StartOfMainMethod
	public static void main(String[] args) 
	{
		int n = 98562;
		myCode(n);
	}
	//EndOfMainMethod
	private static void myCode(int n)
	{
		String s1=String.valueOf(n);
		char []s2=s1.toCharArray();
		System.out.println(s2[0]+" "+s2[s2.length-1]);
	}
}

output : First digit: 9
         last digit : 2
